      <span class="stage-meta-key">Objective</span>
      <span class="stage-meta-val">Gentle re-engagement; acknowledge the patient may still be considering. Prompt to call or book.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="note" style="margin-top:8pt;"><strong>Content team brief:</strong> Warm, unhurried tone. Acknowledge that initial consultations can feel like a big step. Reiterate that the team is available. No hard sell. Reference the phone number and reply option. Approximately 80–120 words.</p>
</div>

<!-- STAGE 04 -->
<div class="stage-card">
  <p class="stage-label">Stage 04 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Enquiry Nurture</p>
