<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════ SECTION 3 ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<h1 id="pre-consult-reminder">3 &nbsp; Pre-Consultation Reminder — Stage 08</h1>
<hr class="section-rule"/>

<p><strong>Automation name in Brevo:</strong> MH — Pre-Consultation Reminder</p>
<p><strong>Entry trigger:</strong> Date-based — fires 72 hours (3 days) before the value stored in <span class="mono">appointment_datetime</span></p>
<p><strong>Brevo configuration note:</strong> In Brevo, set this as a <em>Date-based automation</em> (under Automation → New → Date-based). Select attribute <span class="mono">appointment_datetime</span>, set the offset to <em>3 days before</em>. This automation must be active for all contacts who have a scheduled appointment (i.e., have the <span class="mono">booked_consult</span> tag and a populated <span class="mono">appointment_datetime</span>).</p>

<!-- STAGE 08 -->
<div class="stage-card">
  <p class="stage-label">Stage 08 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Pre-Consultation Reminder</p>
  <p class="stage-title">72-Hour Reminder — Email + SMS</p>
  <div class="stage-meta">
    <div class="stage-meta-row">
      <span class="stage-meta-key">Timing</span>
      <span class="stage-meta-val">72 hours (3 days) before <span class="mono">appointment_datetime</span></span>
    </div>
    <div class="stage-meta-row">
      <span class="stage-meta-key">Channel</span>
      <span class="stage-meta-val">Email (immediately) + SMS (simultaneously or within 5 minutes)</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stage-meta-row">
      <span class="stage-meta-key">Subject line</span>
      <span class="stage-meta-val"><em>Upcoming consultation reminder — Meridian Health</em></span>
    </div>
    <div class="stage-meta-row">
      <span class="stage-meta-key">Template name</span>
      <span class="stage-meta-val">MH — Email 08 — Pre-Consultation Reminder [STUB]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stage-meta-row">
      <span class="stage-meta-key">Objective</span>
      <span class="stage-meta-val">Prompt the patient to complete outstanding forms before the consultation. Confirm appointment details. Reduce no-shows.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<h3>Email 08 — Content Brief (Stub)</h3>
<div class="email-block">
  <p class="email-body">
    <p class="note"><strong>Content team brief:</strong> Remind the patient their consultation is in 72 hours. Confirm date, time, clinician, and location (conditional face-to-face vs telehealth, same logic as Email 02). List outstanding pre-consultation requirements (forms, referral, pathology). Include direct link to the Patient Registration Form if available. Tone: helpful, not alarmist. Approximately 100–150 words.</p>
    <p><strong>Required merge tags:</strong> <span class="mono">contact.FIRSTNAME</span>, <span class="mono">contact.CLINICIAN</span>, <span class="mono">contact.APPOINTMENT_DATE</span>, <span class="mono">contact.APPOINTMENT_TIME</span></p>
    <p><strong>Conditional blocks:</strong> face_to_face vs telehealth (same as Email 02 — reuse template blocks)</p>
  </p>
</div>

<h3>SMS 08 — Reminder Message</h3>
<div class="email-block">
  <p class="email-body">
    Reminder: your Meridian consultation is on {{ contact.APPOINTMENT_DATE }} at {{ contact.APPOINTMENT_TIME }}. Please ensure your forms are completed before your appointment. Questions? Call (03) 9416 4418.
  </p>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════ SECTION 4 ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<h1 id="post-consultation">4 &nbsp; Post-Consultation Automation — Stage 09</h1>
<hr class="section-rule"/>

<p><strong>Automation name in Brevo:</strong> MH — Post-Consultation</p>
<p><strong>Entry trigger:</strong> Tag <span class="mono">consult_completed</span> is applied to contact (applied by admin after consultation is marked complete)</p>

<!-- STAGE 09 -->
<div class="stage-card">
  <p class="stage-label">Stage 09 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Post-Consultation</p>
  <p class="stage-title">Next Steps Email</p>
  <div class="stage-meta">
    <div class="stage-meta-row">
      <span class="stage-meta-key">Timing</span>
      <span class="stage-meta-val">Immediate — on tag <span class="mono">consult_completed</span> applied</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stage-meta-row">
      <span class="stage-meta-key">Channel</span>
      <span class="stage-meta-val">Email</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stage-meta-row">
      <span class="stage-meta-key">Subject line</span>
      <span class="stage-meta-val"><em>Your next steps with Meridian</em></span>
    </div>
    <div class="stage-meta-row">
      <span class="stage-meta-key">Template name</span>
